ỷ Dậu thu Ngô Hưng chu trung tác - 石州慢－己酉秋吳興舟中作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-C%C3%A1n/author-XtDwgc81LrI5SWqmLkXQ1Q">Trương Nguyên Cán</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/Th%C3%A1i-tang-n%E1%BB%AF/poem-hDGyUtjV1UCdVyb6-cY9JA">Thái tang nữ - 採桑女</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-Ng%E1%BA%A1n-Khi%C3%AAm/author-0IgWRHCvEyX64lV-HaskRg">Đường Ngạn Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-ca-%C4%91%E1%BA%A7u/poem-cG1xk5Z4_dk8cIpXZBlXEA">Thuỷ điệu ca đầu - 水調歌頭</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-Chu-V%C4%83n-An/poem-w0GgquYtfAVcoL3oiMfAsQ">Vịnh Chu Văn An - 詠朱文安</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Khuy%E1%BA%BFn/author-JHbQVfC53E2lRJL-xE616A">Nguyễn Khuyến</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
